725034f.title: Queens: 14th Avenue - Parsons Boulevard
725034f.text:
14th Avenue, at Parsons Boulevard, showing a police signal
tation and the site where Parsons Boulevard was later cut
through to extend north to the East River.
P. L. Sperr  Aprih 13, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS

725033f-a.title: Queens: 14th Avenue - Parsons Boulevard
725033f-a.text:
14th Avenue, south side, between Parsons Boulevard and
146th Street, showing, at the above location, the D.M. Talmadge
mansion of 1873 and 1891.
P. L. Sperr  March 3, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIONS
